name: Pepper
description:
Pepper is a handcrafted doll with a spunky retro hairdo with a side pony tail and sweet freckled face. She's wearing a darling floral print dress with a bib front and buttons.  She has wool blend felt collar and blond hair. Her face and collar are embroidered by hand, and her shoes are attached. Pepper is a wonderful playmate for your little one, a fun photography prop and she's also adorable as a display.

18" tall. Stuffed with poly-fill. This doll is not recommended for children under 3 or those who still put toys in their mouths.

Ready to ship.
made from 100% cotton designer quilting fabrics
